        <abstract> 
<p>Sends a sheet of proofs. Will hold four others until he hears from VOK, because of expensive postage. Thinks illustrating Russian translation [of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>] with woodcuts from A. E. Brehm’s work [<hi rend="italic">Illustrirtes Thierleben</hi>, 4 vols. (1864–7)] is an excellent idea.</p> 
